EXTRACT TO C:PROGRAM FILES\STEAM\STEAMAPPS\username of steam account\Ccounter-Strike:Source\cstrike\maps\

TO GET TO BUYZONES...

CTS - go left from spawn into the water swim to the end of tunnel  U GET TELEPORTED TO BUYZONE

TS   - turn around in spawn and go into tunnel                             U GET TELEPORTED TO BUYZONE

To Get Out of Buyzones...

CTS - go straight in buyzone, turn right and go into tunnel             U GET TELEPORTED TO SPAWN

TS   - go straight to end of buyzone                                            U GET TELEPORTED TO SPAWN

HIT E ON SECRET DOORS TO OPEN THEM!!!
